c: 2
v: 251
t: "Ngakho-ke banqoba ngentando kaMvelinqangi futhi uDavide wabulala uGoliyathi futhi uMvelinqangi wamnika ubukhosi nokuhlakanipha wamfundisa kulokho ayekufisa. Futhi ukube kwakungesikona ukuthi uMvelinqangi ugudluza abanye abantu ngabanye, umhlaba wawuzokonakala kodwa uMvelinqangi ungonobubele emihlabeni"